description:
Hungry much? Whether you’re chilling at home, hustling at work, or simply too comfy to cook, Foodmandu has you covered! As Nepal’s first and leading food delivery service app we are here to make your life (and lunch) extra special.

Here’s why you should download us right away:
 
Explore diverse categories & cuisines from 1000+ popular restaurants across Kathmandu, Lalitpur, Bhaktapur, Butwal, Chitwan, and Pokhara.


Order from our exclusive restaurants like Workshop Eatery, Bricks Café, Burger Shack, Koto, Le Trio, Pho 99, Chatime Nepal, Queens, and many more.


Pay your way via QR codes, wallets, debit/credit cards, or cash on delivery (COD).


Stock up on daily essentials and fresh groceries instantly with Foodmandu OneMart! Currently delivering in selected locations. Don’t worry if we're not in your area yet—we're expanding soon, and your neighborhood will be next! Stay tuned for updates!


Join 500,000+ happy foodies who trust Foodmandu and spend your time doing what you love while we take care of the rest!


Download the app and order now for a seamless food delivery experience!

BHOJ (Previously Bhojdeals) is a One stop mobile app for all the foodies in Nepal, where they can search for their favourite restaurants, get food delivered to their home or office, get awesome deals when they dine-in at the restaurants, read and post restaurant reviews, explore restaurant menu, earn credits to their BhojWallet and much more. You name it!

BHOJ is also a strong platform for restaurants in Nepal who want to reach out to hungry foodies. Listing on Bhoj App is a very simple process and doesnt take more than a few minutes. If you are a restaurant, feel free to log on to our website (www.bhojdeals.com) and register yourself.

Key Mobile App features include:

1. Get food delivered from your favourite restaurants. Choose restaurants ''Within zone'' to get delivery in minutes! No minimum order. Order as much or as little as you like!

2. Earn credits to your Bhoj Wallet every time you order using Bhoj App. When you have enough credits, you can use them to pay for your next order. How cool is that!

3. Prefer to dine-in instead? No worries! Grab Free Deal from Bhoj App and get awesome discounts when you visit the restaurant. Simply show saved deal in the app to the restaurant and find savings in your cravings!

4. Want to make decision based on user ratings and menu? Explore user ratings and restaurant menu in Bhoj App before ordering or dining in. If you would like to give your feedback to the restaurants, go ahead post your feedback in the app. After all, everyone likes to have quality food! 

5. Use Advanced Sort & Filter and Near me functionalities to explore restaurants near you based on your preferred cuisine or location.

6. Lastly, dont forget to Refer BhojCode to your friends. They get discounts when they order using your code and you get more credits in your BhojWallet. Start sharing and saving!

7. Thats it! Time to start exploring the app and find out more..

If you have a suggestion for us then please rate our app or simply email us at info@bhojdeals.com. We would really appreciate your constructive feedback. Enjoy using the BHOJ app!

#Bhoj #Bhojdeals #FoodDelivery #Nepal #RestaurantsKathmandu #FoodDeliveryKathmandu #DeliveryApp

BhojMandu is a food delivery company that is committed to providing customers with the best quality food experience. We have been to provide customers with convenient and fast access to best meals, without having to leave the comfort of their own homes. We provide easy-to-use and cost-effective solutions to customers and restaurants & excellent customer service and support to customers and restaurants & we continually strive to improve the customer experience.



Objectives:

Our objective is to provide an easy and efficient way to order, prepare, and deliver food to customers quickly and safely. We strive to make sure that our customers have access to the freshest and most delicious food available. We also make sure that our food is always prepared in a clean and safe environment, with the highest standards of quality and hygiene. We are dedicated to creating a positive customer experience by offering a wide selection of food from our registered restaurant partners.

Key Mobile App features

1.FREE DELIVERY: Get food delivered from your favourite restaurants. Choose restaurants ''Within zone'' to get delivery in 45 minutes! No minimum order. Order as much or as little as you like! Free Delivery for all orders more than Rs.2000.



2. EARN LOYALTY POINTS: Every time you order using BhojMandu App you will get loyalty points credited to your account & you can convert the loyalty points in wallet amount in simple way. 



3. WALLET METHOD: No need to worries! About to pay every time to enter your payment gateway login credentials, we have wallet option you can simply load fund and get extra bonus after fund load is successfully then, you can pay easily through our wallet with hassle FREE!



4. REFER & EARN: Invite your friends, family & businesses & you made extra earning through your REFERAL Code & you can simply convert your referral points in amount.



5. HOT DEALS & OFFERS: Use our app & you will see in homepage of app Today’s Hot Deals & you will order and enjoy with best deals & offers in our app.



6. ORDER SUBSCRIPTION: It’s first time in Nepal, if you are working in an office of any fixed location and you are looking for foods or meals as Daily, Weekly, Monthly wise then we have solution for you. You can subscribe through our app & enjoy with your order.



7. ORDER SCHEDULING: If you will be busy on your work then you can simply order as Order Scheduling, and you will get your order at your selected time.


8. LIVE CHAT: If you have any suggestion or problem simply you can Chat with our agent through our app.


Thats it! Time to start Ordering..

If you have a suggestion for us then please rate our app or simply email us at info@bhojmandu.com. We would really appreciate your feedback. Enjoy using the BhojMandu app!

Get food delivery to your doorstep from thousands of amazing local and national restaurants. Find the meal you crave and order food from restaurants easily with the Uber Eats app. Track your order in real-time.

AVAILABLE INTERNATIONALLY

When you want pizza, you really want pizza. Luckily, our app is the quickest and easiest way to order one with a whole host of exclusive features. Want to know more? Course you do…


ORDER PIZZA

Scroll through our easy-order menu and treat yourself to an all-time classic or discover something new! You can even Create Your Own customised creation, give it a name and save it for next time. 


DELIVERY OR TAKEAWAY

Whether you want to collect from your local store or have your pizza delivered to your door, our app’s got you covered. With stores up and down the country, you’re sure to find a Domino’s Pizza near you. 


EXCLUSIVE PIZZA DEALS

If deals are your thing, you’ve come to the right place (almost). Download our app and you’ll find dozens of exclusive pizza deals to suit any budget (and any occasion). You can even add your vouchers to bag discounts on your order!


GROUP ORDERING

If you need to order pizza for the whole fam, you can set up a group order to make ordering for the gang a doddle. Just send them an invite, let them choose what they want and it’ll get added to the order! 


PRE-ORDERING

Oh, and when it comes to settling up, you can pay pretty much however you like…using card, PayPal or with just a few taps thanks to Apple Pay. Plus, you can keep an eye on your pizza’s progress with our trusty pizza tracker.
 

So, if you haven’t downloaded our app yet, you’re missing out on everything you love about Domino’s and so much more.

Need groceries or essentials delivered? Bolt Market brings everyday items like milk, bread, and coffee, as well as speciality products like pet supplies, cosmetics, or alcohol, right to your doorstep. Forget the long supermarket queues and shop smarter with Bolt Market.

With Bolt Plus, you can access exclusive benefits that save you time and money. For example, you can enjoy priority delivery for your orders, even during the busiest hours.

*GO OUT AND SAVE WITH DINEOUT
As convenient as it is to get food delivered to your door, some moments are worth making the trip out for. Find tables at nearby DineOut restaurants and get a discount off your meal. Just open the app, search for what you crave, and switch to the DineOut tab for in-restaurant offers.

Order meals and snacks from your favourite local and national restaurants, or get groceries, essentials and alcohol delivered to your door.
New users get 30% off your first 3 orders. T&C apply: New users only. Expires 30 days from new user’s first DoorDash order. Valid at participating stores only. 1 redemption per user for each category; national chain, local and grocery (3 in total). Max $20 discount per order. Fees apply.
YOUR FAVOURITE RESTAURANTS
Explore a wide variety of cuisines and get your meals faster with quick and easy ordering. From your local noodle place to your daily coffee fix to your go-to comfort food, find your favourites on DoorDash. National partners include McDonald's, Pizza Hut, Hungry Jack's, Subway, Domino's, KFC, Subway, Taco Bell, Nando's, Oporto, Grill'd, Sushi Sushi, Zambrero and more.
GROCERIES AND CONVENIENCE
Order from your local Coles, IGA or 7-Eleven and have thousands of items delivered when you need them. Top up the pantry, grab last-minute ingredients, stock up on snacks to share with mates or cool down with a slurpee. Get your groceries and everyday essentials delivered with DoorDash.
SUBSCRIBE TO DASHPASS AND SAVE
With a DashPass subscription, enjoy unlimited deliveries and pay $0 delivery fees at DashPass merchants (min. spend applies), plus get access to special offers from local restaurants.
DELIVERY OR PICKUP?
Get what you need straight to your door, schedule delivery for when it's most convenient for you, or order ahead with pickup for a fast and easy takeaway.
NO-CONTACT DELIVERY
Deliveries are left at your door, unless you choose "Hand it to me" when ordering. For contactless deliveries, your Dasher will leave your food in a safe place and let you know it's ready.
TRACK YOUR ORDER
Real-time tracking lets you see when your order will arrive. We've factored in food prep and handling times, traffic, weather and more so you'll know exactly when to set the table.
CONVENIENT PAYMENT
Pay with Apple Pay, credit or debit card, PayPal or Afterpay.
ABOUT DOORDASH
DoorDash is a technology company that connects people with the best in their cities. Since 2013, we've been building products and services to empower local businesses and in turn, generate new ways for people to earn, work and live.
